Here's how you can fix it in Tundra programming language. In this case, we 
should convert strings to numbers before arithmetic operations using parseN
parseNumber function. 

```tundra
val account = {
  name: "Ada",
  billing: {
    current: "30",
    previous: "12"
  }
};

val charge = parseNumber(account.billing.previous);
val fee = 5;
val total = charge + fee;

print(total);
```
